<T>__{cut to:}
<A>__{tight on a turbine as it starts to turn. its rising whine carries over }
<T>__{a series of rhythmic cuts:}
<A>__{magazines are slammed into automatic weapons. ammo belts are fed into rotary cannons. missiles are attached to gunship stub wings. tight on blue hands sharpening wooden arrows. stringing bows. cinching direhorse harnesses. troopers drop into ampsuit cockpits. pilots close gunship canopies. troopers run up shuttle ramps. long lens stack, tight and abstract on gunships as they rise in a swarm amid boiling turbine exhaust and blasting rotor wash.}
